Codegen safe-minifies js`…`/css`…` attribute values (indentation stripped, safe
minifier keeps newlines / ASI). Holey js is left unminified. The corpus runs the
built-in safe pass (JSMinify/CSSMinify on, no fullmin ext).

-- input.gsx --
package views

component Widget() {
	<div
		x-data=js"{
			open: false,
			active: -1,
		}"
		style=css`
			color: red;
			margin: 0;
		`
	></div>
}

-- invoke --
Widget()
-- diagnostics.golden --
-- render.golden --
<div x-data="{
open: false,
active: -1,
}" style="color: red;margin: 0;"></div>
